note_57e9b.text: double click on the canvas to create a note

note_7adef.text: type text and then press Enter

note_4970f.text: click on an item to select it

note_05cbf.text: double click on a note to edit it's text

note_57104.text: click on the squares to change it's color

note_9c467.text: click on the red X to delete it

note_91268.text: click and drag to move it around

note_2e9f1.text: you can also resize it by dragging the corner

note_7ed80.text: right click and drag from one item to another to draw a line between them

note_62bb7.text: do it again to remove the line

note_f7157.text: click and drag on the canvas to pan the screen

note_a39d4.text: use the import and export buttons on the top left to save your layout

note_f80de.text: ctrl-v with an image on your clipboard to paste an image

note_5dd53.text: press enter or escape to finish editing
